530
01:12:38,760 --> 01:12:42,760
<i>Well, it's about Ama.</i>

531
01:12:44,180 --> 01:12:45,350
What?

532
01:12:45,470 --> 01:12:48,930
<i>Back in September, did he get
into some kind of trouble?</i>

533
01:12:53,770 --> 01:12:55,270
I have no idea.

534
01:12:57,610 --> 01:12:58,610
Why?

535
01:12:58,900 --> 01:13:03,780
